### Readiness Check

```jac
walker ready {
    can check with Root entry {
        db_ok = check_database();
        cache_ok = check_cache();

        if db_ok and cache_ok {
            report {"status": "ready"};
        } else {
            report {
                "status": "not_ready",
                "db": db_ok,
                "cache": cache_ok
            };
        }
    }
}
```

